I've ever seen.

1347
01:25:03,306 --> 01:25:06,070
Dixie, have you been serving
that tripe quiche again?

1348
01:25:06,142 --> 01:25:08,804
How come you're not wearing your fur?
I thought you were off tonight.

1349
01:25:08,878 --> 01:25:11,108
